                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Solidarity."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " The worthy must respect the worthy. In the afterlife, all will be united in goal and action. (Oketra)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
